			*nix installation

*) Extract muddy:
	tar xfz mud.tar.gz

*) Configure Makefile's in mud/src and in mud/src/lib. Read
   this files and comment/uncomment require lines.

*) Compile muddy libs:
	cd mud/src/lib
	make

*) Compile muddy
	cd mud/src
	make

*) Edit mud/src/startup and change "home" value to dir, which
   be your muddy root

*) Start muddy:
	mud/src/startup
	
	or
	
	mud/src/muddy -p 4000
	
	or
	
	src/muddy -p 4000

*) Examine logfile in mud/log

*) `telnet localhost 4000` and join ! :)

